  "texts": [
    "Since the release of GPT-3, Open AI's generative language model, in July 2020, there has been a renewed interest in strategizing prompts that can then be fed to applications based on GPT to produce effective content more efficiently.",
    "However, most strategies are based on trials and tests to establish best practices for prompt design.",
    "None of them are grounded in theories that are foundational to effective writing.",
    "This article is an attempt to initiate conversations by blending the architectural workflow of algorithms with writing studies research for effective content generation.",
    "Before diving into prompt engineering, we wanted to bring forth some applications that make research on prompt engineering more important than ever."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}